> ' Доверять секрет недостойному - всё равно, что носить зерно в дырявой сумке. ','auth' => ' <span title= ><b>African proverb</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://www.123rf.com/photo_10242720_wheat-falling-from-a-hole-in-the-bag.html">123rf.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '16','eng' => 'mistrust','trans' => 'ˌmɪsˈtrʌst','rus' => 'не доверять','qeng' => ' Always mistrust a subordinate who never finds fault with his superior. ','qrus' => ' Не верь подчинённому, который никогда не находит недостатков у начальства. ','auth' => ' <span title=(1789–1853),&nbsp;Scottish&nbsp;publisher><b>William Collins</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://www.impactlab.net/2011/04/26/61-of-baby-boomers-say-age-is-not-an-issue-at-work/">impactlab.net</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '16','eng' => 'envy','trans' => 'ˈɛnvɪ','rus' => 'зависть/завидовать','qeng' => ' Do not envy a sinner; you don&rsquo;t know what disaster awaits him. ','qrus' => ' Не завидуй грешнику; ты не знаешь, какая беда ждёт его. ','auth' => ' <span title= ><b>Bible, Old Testament</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://thomastoons.typepad.com/thomastoons_cartoon_blog/2007/10/saturday-evenin.html">thomastoons.typepad.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '16','eng' => 'treachery','trans' => 'ˈtrɛtʃərɪ','rus' => 'предательство','qeng' => ' Trickery and treachery are the practices of fools that have not the wits enought to be honest. ','qrus' => ' Обман и предательство - практика дураков, которым не хватает ума чтобы быть честными. ','auth' => ' <span title=(1706-1790),&nbsp;American&nbsp;statesman,&nbsp;scientist,&nbsp;philosopher,&nbsp;printer,&nbsp;writer&nbsp;and&nbsp;inventor><b>Benjamin Franklin</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://leoff-member.com/2012/04/">leoff-member.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '16','eng' => 'fidelity','trans' => 'fɪˈdɛlɪtɪ','rus' => 'верность','qeng' => ' It will not do to investigate the subject of religion too closely, as it is apt to lead to