odish.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '17','eng' => 'outsider','trans' => 'ˌaʊtˈsaɪdə','rus' => 'посторонний','qeng' => ' Revenge feels right only to those directly involved. Justice feels right even to outsiders. ','qrus' => ' Месть приятна тому, кто её осуществляет. Правосудие радует и посторонних. ','auth' => ' <span title=(b.&nbsp;1946),&nbsp;American&nbsp;magazine&nbsp;columnist,&nbsp;author,&nbsp;lecturer,&nbsp;and&nbsp;playwright><b>Marilyn vos Savant</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://www.kavkaz-uzel.ru/articles/204315/">kavkaz-uzel.ru</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '17','eng' => 'involvement','trans' => 'ɪnˈvɒlvmənt','rus' => 'участие, вовлечение','qeng' => ' The difference between involvement and commitment is like ham and eggs. The chicken is involved; the pig is committed. ','qrus' => ' Разница между участием и совершением - как ветчина и яйца. Курицу вовлекли в дело, а со свиньёй его совершили. ','auth' => ' <span title=(b.1956),&nbsp;Czech&nbsp;born&nbsp;American&nbsp;tennis&nbsp;player><b>Martina Navratilova</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://frugalfisherman.blogspot.com/2011/06/monday-morning-ponderism_20.html">frugalfisherman.blogspot.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '17','eng' => 'disciple','trans' => 'dɪˈsaɪpəl','rus' => 'ученик, последователь','qeng' => ' When we live habitually with the wicked, we become either their victim or their disciple. ','qrus' => ' Привыкнуть жить со злыми людьми, становишься либо жертвой, либо учеником. ','auth' => ' <span title=(1780&nbsp;-&nbsp;1832),&nbsp;English&nbsp;sportsman&nbsp;and&nbsp;writer><b>Charles Colton</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://thegeekwhisperer.com/2009/08/">thegeekwhisperer.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '17','eng' => 'favor','trans' => 'ˈfeɪvə','rus' => 'услуга, помощь','qeng' => ' Don&rsquo;t ask a man for a favor before he has had his lunch. ','qrus' => ' Не проси человека об услуге, пока он не пообедал. ','auth' => ' <span title= 