lɪtɪ','rus' => 'вероятность, правдоподобие','qeng' => ' The truth of a proposition has nothing to do with its credibility. And vice versa. ','qrus' => ' Истинность предположения не имеет ничего общего с его правдоподобностью. И наоборот. ','auth' => ' <span title=(1907-1988),&nbsp;American&nbsp;science&nbsp;fiction&nbsp;writer><b>Robert Heinlein</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://donklephant.com/2007/07/05/americas-love-affair-with-science/">donklephant.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '34','eng' => 'doubtful','trans' => 'ˈdaʊtfʊl','rus' => 'сомнительный','qeng' => ' Even doubtful accusations leave a stain behind them. ','qrus' => ' Даже сомнительные обвинения оставляют за собой пятно. ','auth' => ' <span title=(1608-1661),&nbsp;British&nbsp;clergyman&nbsp;and&nbsp;writer><b>Thomas Fuller</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://enpremierepage.wordpress.com/2012/01/05/is-a-tweet-like-a-stain/">enpremierepage.wordpress.com</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '34','eng' => 'refute','trans' => 'rɪˈfjuːt','rus' => 'опровергать','qeng' => ' Even after the accusation or rumour has been refuted, a suspicion nonetheless lingers. ','qrus' => ' Даже если слух опровергнут, подозрение остаётся. ','auth' => ' <span title= ><b>Swedish Proverb</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://androidactivist.org/news/samsung-google-galaxy-nexus-prime-rumor-round-3-fight/">androidactivist.org</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '34','eng' => 'nonsense','trans' => 'ˈnɒnsəns','rus' => 'бред, чушь','qeng' => ' Sin lies only in hurting other people unnecessarily. All other sins are invented nonsense. ','qrus' => ' Единственный грех - причинение другим вреда без необходимости. Все прочие грехи - придуманный бред. ','auth' => ' <span title=(1907-1988),&nbsp;American&nbsp;science&nbsp;fiction&nbsp;writer><b>Robert Heinlein</b></span><br>Photo:<br><a href="http://www.witnessthis.co.za/2008/07/30/debunking-xenophobia/">witnessthis.co.za</a> ','state' => '1'],['category_id' => '